		<ul class="list-inside list-disc">
			<li>Troubleshot complex software and hardware issues: billing, subscriptions, warranty claims, device replacements.</li>
			<li>Coordinated with cross-functional teams to expedite resolution of complex cases, reducing escalations by 15%.</li>
			<li>Maintained high customer satisfaction by passing monthly quality checks and monitoring evaluations.</li>
		</ul>
		<h2 class="title text-lg"><a class="min-w-[120px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">2020-20</a> Technical Support T1 - Apple</h2>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc">
			<li>Provided front-line technical support with a 95% customer satisfaction rate, efficiently addressing software issues.</li>
			<li>Successfully passed a rigorous skills test, leading to a promotion to the IT Technician team.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
